snippet.title: Final Profit: A Shop RPG - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.finalprofit.com.au/

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1705140/Final_Profit_A_Shop_RPG/
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/FinalProfitRPG

You are Biz, former Queen of Faeona. An organisation called the Bureau of Business threatens the order of your kingdom. Starting from scratch, can you earn enough money to take them on and save your people? Or will you lose sight of your goal on the way?
